[00:51:18.880 --> 00:51:22.880]   But God still moved powerfully in his ministry.
[00:51:22.880 --> 00:51:26.880]   God changed the lives of thousands of people
[00:51:26.880 --> 00:51:30.880]   in the early America.
[00:51:30.880 --> 00:51:37.880]   Be a great preacher.
[00:51:37.880 --> 00:51:41.880]   And if you can, adapt to the culture.
[00:51:41.880 --> 00:51:43.880]   But in the end, be a great preacher
[00:51:43.880 --> 00:51:49.880]   by listening out for what God wants you to be as a preacher.
[00:51:49.880 --> 00:51:53.880]   Be the person that God wants you to be,
[00:51:53.880 --> 00:51:55.880]   not what AI wants you to be.
[00:51:55.880 --> 00:51:57.880]   Thank you.
[00:51:57.880 --> 00:52:04.880]   [applause]
